textBeforeTable: A time-bending futuristic cop performs battle against a stronger copy of himself hailing from a parallel universe. ABSTRACT A groundbreaking form of transportation between parallel universes known as "quantum tunneling" is naturally used and abused by nefarious elements of society, prompting the creation of the Multi-Verse Authorities, police officers charged with apprehending transdimensional lawbreakers. All hell breaks loose when masterful MVA agent Gabriel Yulaw goes rogue, traveling through parallel universes to gain power by killing his copies and leaving the Gabriel in our own world to attempt to stop him from becoming a demigod. Director: James Wong Writers: Glen Morgan; James Wong Music by: Trevor Rabin Producers: Glen Morgan; Steve Chasman Keywords: Sci-Fi, Martial Arts (2-Nov-2001) The One All Names Living people Dead
